Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.43,0:00:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明才剛剛結束期末考試
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.35,0:00:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還想要把我逼上絕路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 分數太低了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.02,0:00:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 那怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.06,0:00:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說 阿虛是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.81,0:00:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好 我要努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.57,0:00:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二年級才剛剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.78,0:00:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧 長門
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.28,0:00:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把長門也扯上 她會困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.66,0:00:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,升級之後我們三人竟然在同一個班
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為長門是令人操心的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.95,0:02:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.91,0:02:20.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.45,0:02:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.37,0:02:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.66,0:02:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您好 打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個人只為了社團活動的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:35.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就登那個坡道過來 真是辛苦你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.13,0:02:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.26,0:02:41.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們也是心甘情願去做的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:45.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要是涼宮要去的地方 我哪裏都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:48.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼問題的話 可以跟我商量哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.69,0:02:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些要裝飾在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼什麼 親自迎接本社長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 為什麼你那麼從容的和老師打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.58,0:03:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光明正大的也要有個限度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 都到現在了你們還在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.01,0:03:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就拿到學校的許可了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.67,0:03:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鏘 看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:29.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來在情人節的時候就已經穿校服過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:36.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,涼宮的外表太引人注目了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷偷進來確實有點困難
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是那樣的話 事先說出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論有沒有許可 反正都是要來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼差別
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很大差別
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 奇怪 我應該跟有希說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長～門～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:03:59.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有希 可以打擾一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:10.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 你繼續玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這上面隨便簽個名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先把各種工作做好 我進來也就容易了 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字寫在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈哈 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:31.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不知道要先糾正你哪一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有太多選擇 我好猶豫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.96,0:04:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 涼子 我早就說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:40.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 你那又算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種像無良商人一樣讓人簽字畫押的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:46.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 箭頭指向這邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:50.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來你就是像元兇一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:53.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們就算是年級升了也要過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:59.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有涼宮好像已經完成計劃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,計劃？不應該是計謀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.95,0:05:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她什麼都沒有告訴你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裏有情報會留給隨從A
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順便一提 你是隨從B
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈哈 我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有一點可以確信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她好像特別高興哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:27.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和去年的涼宮完全沒辦法比
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的在反省嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個樣子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}兩位都別吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 非常的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的真的在反省嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.86,0:05:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:45.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 只要那傢伙高興
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.20,0:05:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只有不好的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 阿虛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鶴屋學姊 為什麼你一臉的成就感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.39,0:06:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在摸索有衝擊力的出場方式
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衝擊過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒表揚你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.23,0:06:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快分開 禁止羞羞的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門 等等 脖子要…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:35.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.42,0:06:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 還好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝比奈 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:49.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門 阿虛 你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 昨天真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:07:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 朝比奈沒有必要道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:02.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 完全沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天鶴屋學姐不在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鶴屋去拿忘掉的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該馬上就回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.95,0:07:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實玖琉 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:19.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿虛 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長萌也還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長萌？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈 書道社員把毛筆忘記了真是不應該呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 阿虛你真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:39.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我不在旁邊 你也和怕生的實玖琉說起話來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這真是不得了的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:44.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克服了最初糟糕的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後到今天這一步 真是值得表揚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:51.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了那個是誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:53.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全就是莫須有的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多可以把你從實玖琉粉絲俱樂部的團員升級成幹部了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.50,0:08:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種事情我可沒聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要做什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:05.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先別說職位了那本來就是誤會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎 長門
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也請告訴我 他們兩個發生了什麼事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你聽了這個說不定會受到打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:23.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使這樣你也要聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要聽 請說給我聽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.94,0:08:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 心意很堅決啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就說了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:37.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是去年12月初
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 這樣就是5個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕快去交給長門吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 永遠不會忘記的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.72,0:08:55.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿虛的羞恥計劃終於實現了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個解說純屬虛構
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:09:00.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與現實中的人物和團體沒有任何關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鶴屋好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒、沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假裝成意外的惡劣行為
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:20.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且阿虛的真正目的還在這之後啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:21.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒有好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}啊——！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時聽見實玖琉悲鳴的我在那裏看到的是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到的是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少年
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:41.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以調皮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是把實玖琉推到的禽獸一般的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸——
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真想變成一個貝殼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.73,0:09:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去解釋這是個誤會的人又多了1個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 讀書？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我教你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:09.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:12.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才發下來的小考成績很不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…我怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.22,0:10:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 阿虛果然是——
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:22.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是比朝倉差啊 別繼續說了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看一下氣氛啊 氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:28.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一開始就來依靠我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對自己是沒好處的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.57,0:10:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝倉 你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學習中最重要的就是應用能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,經歷了各種煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:42.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後找到通向正解的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:47.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實最快的方法是找會的人問
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你不覺得最快並不是最好的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.30,0:10:56.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:10:58.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 你明白了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找別人問
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:03.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了隨你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.39,0:11:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門怎麼樣啊 那傢伙看起來腦袋很好的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去問一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.78,0:11:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 長門
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍一微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:21.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙干…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來教你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是剛才…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來教你 你是學生 OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, your highness
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:33.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為交換
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:37.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不許向長門提起讀書的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:39.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道 剛剛的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:55.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:11:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來好像要親的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:08.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實只是吹掉眼睛裏進的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.49,0:12:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種漫畫一般的設定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:14.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能看到真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:18.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門這大概和你想的不太一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼要開始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛要換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為想換 就是要這個氣氛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹勁十足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要讀書嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝啊 但是沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是一些像 複習一樣的東西而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.95,0:12:44.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門就繼續玩遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可、可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.57,0:12:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.08,0:12:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用在意我們哦 長門
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就不多說什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:55.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就從這裏開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一開始就做這麼難的問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:13:01.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 阿虛還真的是笨…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 別說了 別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.84,0:13:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀吼 我來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.10,0:13:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼聚精會神在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 原來在讀書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 我可是很熱愛讀書的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 熱愛讀書呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是那樣的話上課認真聽一下不是基本都能明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:26.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不是值得熱愛的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:31.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是光陽園太厲害了 還是你太奇怪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種情況請你說涼宮同學太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且為什麼要複習去年的範圍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯確實 很久以前做過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:48.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.85,0:13:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:52.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該死的升學學校讓人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們太礙事了 回去吧 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:14:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿虛 這樣就洩氣了我們還怎麼繼續啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:03.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才沒有洩氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.48,0:14:08.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是咬牙切齒地感嘆一下學校間的差距為何如此之大而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:10.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不甘心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:15.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝倉你沒關係嗎被這麼瞧不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.71,0:14:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為北高的代表
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被指定成代表了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊 就是代表！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為北高優等生兼班長的朝倉涼子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且就連「下一屆學生會長就是朝倉吧」這樣的傳言都存在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.09,0:14:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然只是很少的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.01,0:14:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次聽說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}涼宮同學 這個放在這裏可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傳說中超級班長就能容忍北高被如此瞧不起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}再往我這移2公分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}我沒有瞧不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傳說！我是傳說！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經成為了北高這麼重要的人物了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 瞧不起北高
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.33,0:14:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就等於瞧不起我這個代表
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,涼宮二啊不 光陽園
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:14:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來做你們的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼快就被激起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:05.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 無所謂了 反而更有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:07.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這場決鬥 我接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那問題就是這一頁的第三題了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:17.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們正在學這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.73,0:15:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裏？我來確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.23,0:15:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 英語問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:26.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,書上寫著數學哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.07,0:15:32.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝倉一定要幫我報仇雪恥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:34.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這完全就是自找的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的是應用能力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.66,0:15:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是沒學到的知識
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就用現在學到的知識解給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哭起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:05.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝倉 夠了 別再做了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種沒學過的題目
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:07.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫不出來也是正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我背負著北高的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 讓你背負了奇怪的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然這樣 我要掀起最後的底牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門 長門
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:28.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼在哭啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:35.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 朝倉 不是說不要向長門請教問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 北高的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.02,0:16:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:46.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那是你解不開的問題啊 拜託長門也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:50.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你給我看著 OK ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, your maiesty
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要解這個問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.99,0:16:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 3吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼快就開啦？! !
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古泉 答案是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:09.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是的 是3
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 我就說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過程都沒有 你亂猜的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有希 給我們講一下詳細過程
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.39,0:17:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把***給*****把出來的*****輕輕的***放上去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.03,0:17:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後***把***和***先揉在一起***
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸？什麼什麼 在說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,揉在一起 到底是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先這到底在說什麼語啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去想也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:47.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門雖然腦子好但解說起來超級爛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:50.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽起來像在講宇宙文
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙文？空間？第一？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:55.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的長門不能給外人看見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.01,0:17:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那爆炸了 然後又聚起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆炸？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:04.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聚集？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對對 然後答案就是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放大 收縮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.82,0:18:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 長門 我今天決定在這吃午餐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說好還是壞呢 好厲害的集中力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你終於發現了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.45,0:19:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈 想拿回去？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過來搶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你欺負人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亂開玩笑的我才有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首…首先我們先分開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.75,0:19:55.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:20:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺我們被誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下原原本本的告訴她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:08.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的便當在朝倉那
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.69,0:20:17.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.65,0:20:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的一半給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的便當一半
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.42,0:20:34.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這難度太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.25,0:20:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不喜歡對吧 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說是好朋友但也有點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:48.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛的態度非常不行啊…呃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然說給我半個便當那個難度太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:21:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以請你從「啊」開始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.36,0:21:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「啊」？!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.36,0:21:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個難度不是更高嗎？長門
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊「啊」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.62,0:21:15.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛長門喜歡就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.38,0:21:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧「啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.22,0:21:25.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑 開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.55,0:21:32.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道長門沒那種膽子耍親熱啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:34.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是長門的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.77,0:21:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.94,0:21:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…我打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.95,0:21:46.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 朝倉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門同學跟阿虛居然「啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請聽我說朝倉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.33,0:21:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不是你想的那樣複雜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.29,0:21:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬要說的話那個蛋卷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.33,0:22:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的老師不是說不能和喜歡吃甜蛋卷的男人結婚什麼的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.63,0:22:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並不是那樣的 中澤…啊不 朝倉同學等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.52,0:23:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.60,0:23:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去合宿旅遊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.81,0:23:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合宿？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.36,0:23:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.23,0:23:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來說的計劃是這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.74,0:23:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門同學你早就知道了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.82,0:23:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.24,0:23:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸？我說過了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.83,0:24:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好期待吧！

